(8382, 'Moxipen 500mg 12 caps.', 'موكسيبن 500 مجم 12 كبسولة', '', '15', 'Amoxicillin', 'Misr', 'Cap', 'كبسولة', 'مضاد حيوي', 'Penicillins.monocomponent', '500mg', 'Amoxicillin alone is indicated to treat susceptible bacterial infections of the ear, nose, throat, genitourinary tract, skin, skin structure, and lower respiratory tract.[L11656,L11659] Amoxicillin is given with calvulanic acid to treat acute bacterial sinusitis, community acquired pneumonia, lower respiratory tract infections, acute bacterial otitis media, skin and skin structure infections, and urinary tract infections.[L11650,L7880,L11653] Amoxicillin is given with omeprazole in the treatment of _Helicobacter pylori_ (_H. pylori_) infection.[L9743,L11647]
Amoxicillin is used in combination with [vonoprazan] and [clarithromycin] as co-packaged triple therapy or in combination with [vonoprazan] as co-packaged dual therapy to treat _H. pylori_ infection in adults.[L41695]', '6221035012163', '', 4538, '2023-03-11', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
